    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m looking for a new home for my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a great companion on the road. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it a perfect pick if you want something dependable and ready to go. It drives super smoothly and is just waiting for its next adventure. Feel free to reach out\u2014I'd love for you to come by and take it for a spin!",
