    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers a perfect balance of spirited performance and everyday reliability. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel\u2014typical of a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; the leather upholstery remains supple, with only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All technological features, including the navigation system and heated seats, are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and has been serviced at regular intervals, with a comprehensive log of oil changes and a recent coolant flush. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This is a solid, honest car that is ready for its next owner to drive away with peace of mind.",
      "price": 34500.0,
