    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my well-loved car. She's been a fantastic companion and is still in really great shape, running smoothly and ready for many more adventures! I've made sure to stay on top of maintenance, so you're getting a reliable ride that still looks sharp on the road. It\u2019s perfect for someone who wants quality without the brand-new price tag. I'd love for you to come by, take a look, and see how great she drives!",
      "price": 32500.0,
