    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp with a 7,900 RPM redline. This example utilizes the Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and the factory M-Variable differential lock for optimal power delivery. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a recent inspection of the rear subframe mounting points and a comprehensive VANOS system refresh. Equipped with staggered 18-inch Style 67 wheels and factory-spec ventilated rotors, the braking system provides consistent bite without fade. The suspension geometry is stock, preserving the original damping characteristics and sharp turn-in response. A mechanically sound specimen for the purist seeking an authentic, analog driving experience.",
